volumeInfo.title: Profiles of Remarkable Businesses (Collection)
volumeInfo.description: "A brand new collection of essential insights for your business and career from world-renowned experts[]now in a convenient e-format, at a great price!" Actionable lessons from a century of extraordinary businesses[from Ford to NetFlix, Wal-Mart to Zappos What you can learn from the world's greatest businesses: from legendary startups to extraordinary turnarounds! Crucial takeaways from the experiences of McDonald's, Home Depot, Zappos, Wal-Mart, Oprah (Harpo), Ford, NetFlix, UPS, Lego, Intuit, and many others. "From world-renowned business profilers New Word City and Nancy F. Koehn."
